returns.declareSpoiltProducts.title = Declare spoilt products from an earlier return
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.heading = Declare spoilt products from an earlier return
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.caption.text = Spoilt vaping products
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.p = Tell us about any vaping products declared in previous returns that have become spoilt.
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.summary = What ‘spoilt products’ and ‘fit for consumption’ mean
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.content.p1 = Spoilt vaping products are products that:
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.content.bullet1 = you have already paid duty on
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.content.and1 = and
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.content.bullet2 = you have destroyed because they are no longer fit for consumption
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.content.p2 = Vaping products are not fit for consumption if they:
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.content.bullet3 = have passed their expiry date
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.content.or1 = or
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.content.bullet4 = have been recalled for safety reasons
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.content.p3 = You do not need to declare vaping products destroyed before duty was paid. These are not considered spoilt products.
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.content.p4 = You must keep a record of destroyed products in your business records.
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.content.p5 = Vaping products that have been returned because they are not selling well, are not considered spoilt products.
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.content.p6.text = If you intend to destroy these products, you may be able to
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.details.content.p6.link = claim the duty back under the excise duty drawback scheme
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.question = Do you have any spoilt vaping products to declare?
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.checkYourAnswersLabel = Declare spoilt products
returns.declareSpoiltProducts.change.hidden = declare spoilt products

returns.selectSpoiltPeriod.title = When did you release the products?
returns.selectSpoiltPeriod.heading = When did you release the products?
returns.selectSpoiltPeriod.caption = Spoilt vaping products
returns.selectSpoiltPeriod.p1 = Tell us which month you released the now-spoilt vaping products, so we can calculate the duty paid.
returns.selectSpoiltPeriod.p2 = You will not be able to claim back more duty than you paid on these products.

