returns.declareDutySuspense.title = Finished vaping products received or moved under duty suspension
returns.declareDutySuspense.heading = Finished vaping products received or moved under duty suspension
returns.declareDutySuspense.caption.text = Report duty suspended vaping products
returns.declareDutySuspense.p = You must tell us if you have received or moved any finished vaping products that were previously stored in an approved place.
returns.declareDutySuspense.details.summary = What does ‘duty suspension’ and ‘approved places’ mean?
returns.declareDutySuspense.details.content.p1 = Duty suspension means you do not have to pay Vaping Products Duty straight away, if your vaping products are stored in approved places.
returns.declareDutySuspense.details.content.p2 = Examples of approved premises are an excise warehouse or a registered store.
returns.declareDutySuspense.details.content.p3 = Vaping Products Duty must be paid when the finished products are taken out of an approved place to be sold or supplied in the UK.
returns.declareDutySuspense.question = Have you received or moved any finished vaping products in duty suspense?
returns.declareDutySuspense.error.required = Select yes if you have received or moved any finished vaping products in duty suspense
returns.declareDutySuspense.checkYourAnswersLabel = Declare duty suspense
