returns.declareAdjustmentQuestion.title = Declare adjustments from earlier returns
returns.declareAdjustmentQuestion.heading = Declare adjustments from earlier returns
returns.declareAdjustmentQuestion.caption = Over or under-declared adjustments
returns.declareAdjustmentQuestion.checkYourAnswersLabel = Do you have any vaping products you need to over or under declare?
returns.declareAdjustmentQuestion.change.hidden = whether you need to declare adjustments
returns.declareAdjustmentQuestion.p1 = Tell us about any vaping products that were over or under-declared in previous returns.
returns.declareAdjustmentQuestion.p2 = You may be required to explain why these were over or under-declared.
returns.declareAdjustmentQuestion.details.summary = What ‘over-declared’ and ‘under-declared’ mean
returns.declareAdjustmentQuestion.details.content.p1 = Over-declared means the quantity you declared is greater than the amount that was released.
returns.declareAdjustmentQuestion.details.content.p2 = For example, you included a despatch twice or declared in the wrong period.
returns.declareAdjustmentQuestion.details.content.p3 = Under-declared means you have declared less leaving the premises than has been released.
returns.declareAdjustmentQuestion.details.content.p4 = For example, you missed a despatch from the accounting record.
returns.declareAdjustmentQuestion.question = Do you have any vaping products you need to over or under declare?

